data.text:
Timbs, John.

London...

London. Lockwood & Company and Richard Bentley. 1865-1868. First Editions. 8 vols. 12mos. Elegantly bound by Riviere in 3/4 gilt ruled morocco, gilt ruled spine compartments, gilt tooled embellishments, gilt tooled raised bands, gilt titles. Marbled end sheets. teg.

This uniformly bound set of Timbs' classic works on London is comprised of the following titles: The Romance of London [3 volumes/1865.] , Walks and Talks About London [1 volume/ 1865], Club Life of London [ 2 volumes/ 1866], London and Westminster [2volumes/1868].

A Very Fine set.Featured Sets.

Item #4925
